00:44:52,000 --> 00:44:58,000
[SPEAKER_00] is to be the most holy eukaristic instruments of reparation.

350
00:44:58,000 --> 00:45:16,000
[SPEAKER_01] Kada čitate vijesti, iziđete na ulice u velikim gradovima,

351
00:45:17,000 --> 00:45:22,000
[SPEAKER_01] vidite ljudi kako zapravo lude.

352
00:45:22,000 --> 00:45:25,000
[SPEAKER_01] Loosen it.

353
00:45:25,000 --> 00:45:28,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ja, haluciniraju.

354
00:45:28,000 --> 00:45:30,000
[SPEAKER_00] No, no, no.

355
00:45:30,000 --> 00:45:33,000
[SPEAKER_00] Loosen sense. Loosen it.

356
00:45:33,000 --> 00:45:35,000
[SPEAKER_01] Aha, loosing it. Ja.

357
00:45:35,000 --> 00:45:37,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ja, i gube razum, gube um.

358
00:45:37,000 --> 00:45:41,000
[SPEAKER_01] I pitate se što mogu učiniti.

359
00:45:42,000 --> 00:45:47,000
[SPEAKER_01] Nitko ne može promijeniti svijet.

360
00:45:47,000 --> 00:45:54,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ali mi možemo učiniti ono što smo pozvani činiti.

361
00:45:54,000 --> 00:46:01,000
[SPEAKER_00] Biti sveta euharistijska posuda.

362
00:46:02,000 --> 00:46:04,000
[SPEAKER_01] i Isus će učiniti ostalo.

363
00:46:04,000 --> 00:46:06,000
[SPEAKER_01] A Isus će učiniti ostalo.

364
00:46:06,000 --> 00:46:10,000
[SPEAKER_01] Kao što je rekao sv. Pavao,

365
00:46:10,000 --> 00:46:14,000
[SPEAKER_01] Pavao je posadio.

366
00:46:14,000 --> 00:46:17,000
[SPEAKER_01] Apollo je zalijevao.

367
00:46:17,000 --> 00:46:22,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ali samo Bog čini da raste.

368
00:46:23,000 --> 00:46:28,000
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle, ja se pripremam za pričest.

369
00:46:28,000 --> 00:46:30,000
[SPEAKER_01] I take communion.

370
00:46:30,000 --> 00:46:32,000
[SPEAKER_01] Pričestim se.

371
00:46:32,000 --> 00:46:35,000
[SPEAKER_01] A Bog će učiniti ostalo.

372
00:46:35,000 --> 00:46:39,000
[SPEAKER_01] I ako samo to činimo,

373
00:46:40,000 --> 00:46:54,000
[SPEAKER_00] smatrajte da ste Božji vojnik poslušan svome pozivu.

374
00:46:54,000 --> 00:47:00,000
[SPEAKER_01] Mi smo vojnici koji smo pozvani.

375
00:47:01,000 --> 00:47:07,000
[SPEAKER_01] a ovo je veliko vrijeme bitke.

376
00:47:07,000 --> 00:47:15,000
[SPEAKER_01] Mi smo usred žestoke bitke.

377
00:47:15,000 --> 00:47:22,000
[SPEAKER_01] I Sotona guta milijune duša.

378
00:47:23,000 --> 00:47:31,000
[SPEAKER_01] Svakog dana mnogo duša biva izgubljeno.

379
00:47:31,000 --> 00:47:35,000
[SPEAKER_01] To je golema tragedija.

380
00:47:35,000 --> 00:47:44,000
[SPEAKER_01] Kad bismo doista znali tu stvarnost,

381
00:47:44,000 --> 00:47:48,000
[SPEAKER_01] bili bismo tako tužni,

382
00:47:49,000 --> 00:48:00,000
[SPEAKER_01] ali bismo zapravo rasli u svom žaru za spašavanje duša.

383
00:48:00,000 --> 00:48:13,000
[SPEAKER_01] Mojte Boga da vam podari pravi žar za duše, pravu gorljivost za duše.

384
00:48:14,000 --> 00:48:18,000
[SPEAKER_01] Kada je Isus umirao na križu,

385
00:48:18,000 --> 00:48:27,000
[SPEAKER_01] jedna od njegovih posljednjih riječi je "žedan sam".

386
00:48:27,000 --> 00:48:32,000
[SPEAKER_01] On nije bio žedan vode.

387
00:48:32,000 --> 00:48:36,000
[SPEAKER_00] Bio je žedan duša.

388
00:48:37,000 --> 00:48:43,000
[SPEAKER_01] i On želi da i mi budemo žedni duša.

389
00:48:43,000 --> 00:48:49,000
[SPEAKER_01] Razlog zbog kojeg sam ja ovdje večera s vama

390
00:48:49,000 --> 00:48:57,000
[SPEAKER_01] je taj što mi je doista stalo do vašeg spasenja.

391
00:48:57,000 --> 00:49:01,000
[SPEAKER_01] Stalo mi je do vaše duše.

392
00:49:02,000 --> 00:49:06,000
[SPEAKER_01] vidio sam vlastitim očima

393
00:49:06,000 --> 00:49:13,000
[SPEAKER_01] kamo duše odlaze kada su izgubljene.

394
00:49:14,000 --> 00:49:21,000
[SPEAKER_01] i ne želim da itko od vas onamo ode.

395
00:49:21,000 --> 00:49:25,000
[SPEAKER_01] Moramo se probuditi.

396
00:49:25,000 --> 00:49:30,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ova je život vrlo kratak.

397
00:49:31,000 --> 00:49:38,000
[SPEAKER_01] i nećemo se ne okrenuti, a bit ćemo u kovčegu.

398
00:49:38,000 --> 00:49:42,000
[SPEAKER_01] I jamčim vas, jamčim vam,

399
00:49:42,000 --> 00:49:47,000
[SPEAKER_01] bolje vam je biti pripravljeni.

400
00:49:48,000 --> 00:49:53,000
[SPEAKER_01] a jedina moguća priprema

401
00:49:53,000 --> 00:49:56,000
[SPEAKER_01] je biti svet.

402
00:49:56,000 --> 00:50:00,000
[SPEAKER_01] Nema druge pripreme.

403
00:50:00,000 --> 00:50:04,000
[SPEAKER_01] Slava Bogu!

